properties.Name: EquifaxConsumerCreditInformationSummary
properties.Description: A summary of all the accounts on file.

Columns.Name: EquifaxConsumerAccountTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Consumer Account Type.

Columns.Name: MemberName
Columns.Description: Member Name indicates the name of the company who holds the listed account. Also displayed is the type of credit held with the named company. The member name is often referred to as the account owner.

Columns.Name: ReportedDate
Columns.Description: The date that information was reported.

Columns.Name: OpenedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Equifax account was opened.

Columns.Name: HighCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The high credit amount for all accounts.

Columns.Name: Terms
Columns.Description: Terms indicates the required payment amount on the listed account.

Columns.Name: BalanceAmount
Columns.Description: Balance indicates the outstanding amount owed on the listed account at the time it was last reported.

Columns.Name: PastDueAmount
Columns.Description: Past Due indicates the payment amount past due as of the date of reporting on the listed account.

Columns.Name: DaysLateReceivingPayment
Columns.Description: 30/60/90 of days indicates the number of times the listed account was 30/60/90+ days late in receiving payment.

Columns.Name: EquifaxConsumerAccountDesignatorTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Consumer Account Designator Type.

Columns.Name: EquifaxPaymentRatingTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Payment Rating Type.
